<strong>data_iso                    added from: file:///data/iso             248
</strong>epel/x86_64                 Extra Packages for Enterprise Linux 7  8,545
extras/7/x86_64             CentOS-7 - Extras                        214
foreman/x86_64              Foreman 1.9                              367
